      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Elves were betrayed during the Gap and can be untrusting of others. These elves train to see through deceptions, and gain a +2 species bonus to @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.nBrYkGfNBJAHe0xJ]{Sense Motive} checks and saving throws against illusion spells. Once per day, they can roll a Sense Motive check twice and use the better result.</p>\n<p><strong>This replaces elven immunities.</strong></p>\n<p><em><strong></strong></em></p><em><strong></strong></em><p><em><strong></strong> Use @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.racial-features.UcZr3VMRQePGITI0]{Elven Skeptic (Sense Motive Double Roll)}<span> for tracking usage of once per day ability.</span></em></p>"
